message.body: Ok. That's who I thought. Thank God I'm actually off for something.
Do you know where?
5:30 at Spasso. 34 South Front Steet.
Wow! I was expecting an I don't know. Haha. I'll look it up.
I thought you would be.
Today had just been crazy! I am so tired my eyes feel like they're going to fall out of my head. Are we watching AHS tonight?
Yeah I'd like to
Ok
Since tomorrow I hope we're putting up the tree, but if not, we might be with friends, did you want to do a date night at max brenner's tonight?
Your computer is so hard to get used to! Haha.

And um. So guess the battery died. I plugged it in and hit the power button. Now it's frozen. Black screen says Lenovo. I'm not going to touch it. God damn these computers! I can't get done what I need to!
See this is a good reason why not to give your computer to someone. Now everything I had open is gone because you didn't charge it.
Oh my god! I had it open for like ten minutes!
It's okay. I made sure to save everything because I knew you were using it. I'm smart like that
I didn't know.
I hate you
Batteries are tricky
Date night please?
Well that sucks, because I love you.
And I would love to go to Max Brenner with you.
Miraculously my Villanova computer has working internet.
Good :) I need to make myself look pretty.
Okay good. So you destroyed my stuff for nothing :P
And yeah make yourself nice and pretty for me
Though all you have to do is wake up and you're already there
Yup. I did. Haha. Oh how you flatter me.
(You like this insult then nice statement then insult then nice statement? It's how you keep ladies on their toes. Confuse them. Make them not know if their mad.)
U
Ugh. I know right. I fall for it all the time. Just like how your such a good liar. I am just hopelessly in love with you.
Haha. Jenny actually cancelled in advance.
I can't stop smiling for very long. I'm excited about tonight! I'm a little giddy.
Haha good!
I'm excited too. And I really want you to try the hot chocolate
